'''Jason Court''' (born [[September 6]], [[1960s#1963|1963]]) is a screen actor known for playing [[Kyle Katarn]] in the full motion video scenes of the video game ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II]]''. His performance of Katarn became the source of the character's looks in all subsequent appearances.

